layer base (~50M players)"]', '["Do not pursue - this is game design feedback, not a market opportunity", "If interested in MTG space, analyze broader pain points (deck building tools, card pricing, tournament organization)", "Redirect analysis toward actual MTG player problems: card authenticity, collection management, trading efficiency"]', 'Grixis Legendary Eternal Commander with Amass/Afflict Synergies', 'Magic: The Gathering players who enjoy Eternal tribal themes lack a dedicated Grixis (Blue-Black-Red) legendary creature that synergizes with Amass and Afflict mechanics. This limits deck-building options for Commander format players who want to build around the flavorful Eternal zombie theme from the Amonkhet block.', '{"original_title" : "I love Eternals - I wish there was a Grixis Legendary Eternal that cares about Amass/Afflict", "original_body" : "", "subreddit" : "r/general", "upvotes" : 170, "comments" : 56, "platform" : "reddit", "url" : "", "confidence_score" : 0.85}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO opportunities (id, title, description, category, subcategory, severity, validation_count, growth_rate, market_size, geographic_scope, country, region, city, completion_status, solution_description, solved_at, solved_by, feasibility_score, duplicate_of, author_id, is_anonymous, status, created_at, updated_at, source_id, source_url, source_platform, ai_analyzed, ai_analyzed_at, ai_opportunity_score, ai_summary, ai_market_size_estimate, ai_competition_level, ai_urgency_level, ai_target_audience, ai_pain_intensity, ai_business_model_suggestions, ai_competitive_advantages, ai_key_risks, ai_next_steps, ai_generated_title, ai_problem_statement, raw_source_data, latitude, longitude, demographics, search_trends, demographics_fetched_at) VALUES (98, 'Samurai - A Like Supreme live 7/15/2077 at Red Dirt', 'This is a true masterpiece, I wish there was more like this in-game', 'Technology & Software', 'cyberpunkgame', 1, 9, 0.9, '$0', 'online', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'open', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, FALSE, 'active', '2025-12-15 17:50:24.226892+00:00', '2025-12-15 23:01:23.911804+00:00', NULL, NULL, NULL, TRUE, '2025-12-17 00:33:36.058022', 72, 'Fan request for fictional in-game music content - not a real business opportunity', '$0', 'n/a', 'low', 'Cyberpunk 2077 video game players', 1, '["This is not a viable business opportunity - it''s fan commentary about fictional content", "The ''problem'' is about wanting more of a specific song from a video game", "No real-world consumer pain point exists here"]', '["None - this is not a legitimate business opportunity"]', '["This submission appears to be misclassified gaming content, not a business opportunity", "The date (2077) and context (Samurai band from Cyberpunk game) indicate fictional content", "No actionable consumer pain point or market demand exists"]', '["Filter out gaming commentary/fan posts from business opportunity pipeline", "Implement better content classification to identify fictional vs. real-world problems", "Focus analysis on posts with clear consumer pain points and real-world applicability"]', 'AI-Generated In-Game Music Expansion Platform', 'Video game players become attached to limited in-game music tracks and desire more similar content that captures the same aesthetic and emotional quality. Current games have finite soundtracks, leaving fans wanting expanded musical experiences that match the game''s atmosphere and style.', '{"original_title" : "Samurai - A Like Supreme live 7/15/2077 at Red Dirt", "original_body" : "This is a true masterpiece, I wish there was more like this in-game", "subreddit" : "r/technology_and_software", "upvotes" : 9, "comments" : 3, "platform" : "reddit", "url" : "", "confidence_score" : 0.85}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL) ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO opportunities (id, title, description, category, subcategory, severity, validation_count, growth_rate, market_size, geographic_scope, country, region, city, completion_status, solution_description, solved_at, solved_by, feasibility_score, duplicate_of, author_id, is_anonymous, status, created_at, updated_at, source_id, source_url, source_platform, ai_analyzed, ai_analyzed_at, ai_opportunity_score, ai_summary, ai_market_size_estimate, ai_competition_level, ai_urgency_level, ai_target_audience, ai_pain_intensity, ai_business_model_suggestions, ai_competitive_advantages, ai_key_risks, ai_next_steps, ai_generated_title, ai_problem_statement, raw_source_data, latitude, longitude, demographics, search_trends, demographics_fetched_at) VALUES (99, 'WWM Helper – mystic tools, local-time timers & full guide index (fan-made site)', 'Quick follow-up to the earlier posts about my WWM Helper site:

- First version: https://www.reddit.com/r/WhereWindsMeet/comments/1pbgp50/i_built_a_small_web_app_for_wwm_timers_and/
- Redesign update: https://www.reddit.com/r/WhereWindsMeet/comments/1pfycu7/updated_my_wwm_helper_site_with_a_new_design/
- Steam guide (same project, more screenshots): https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=3618522349

**Site:** https://besaids.github.io/WWM-Helper/  
Fan-made, no ads, no login; your data stays in your browser.

---

## What’s new since the last post

**1. Local-time reset handling**

- All the old “21:00 UTC” style resets now show in your **local time**, including weekday rollover.
- Daily/weekly checklist descriptions were updated so you don’t have to mentally convert Friday 21:00 UTC anymore.

**2. Mystic tools**

- **Mystic Upgrade Planner**  
  https://besaids.github.io/WWM-Helper/tools/mystic-upgrade-planner  
  Plan mystic upgrades, see total material costs, and compare “damage gained vs mats spent” so you don’t sink mats into trash.

- **Mystic Metrics – Efficiency / Vitality analysis**  
  https://besaids.github.io/WWM-Helper/guides/mystic-metrics  
  Interactive scatter chart for mystic skills; X = vitality cost, Y = damage per vitality, bubble size = total damage. You can highlight strong skills and pin the ones you care about.

- **Mystic Skill Materials guide**  
  https://besaids.github.io/WWM-Helper/guides/mystic-skill-materials  
  Focuses on flowers/materials used for mystic upgrades so you can farm them over time instead of getting stuck later.
